There is a 'Makefile'.
On writing the command 'make' in the terminal it creates an executable of the name 'carrom'
The source code's name is '201302063_carrom.cpp'

glut.h and gl.h need to be installed before running this program.

The Header Files used are:
#include <iostream>
#include <stdio.h>
#include <sys/time.h>
#include <stdlib.h>
#include <cmath>
#include <sstream>  //include this to use string streams
#include <string> 
#ifdef __APPLE__
#include <OpenGL/OpenGL.h>
#include <GLUT/glut.h>
#else
#include <GL/glut.h>
#endif
